OL,4,Cscandal yet to receive compensation
OL,6,FA Gateshead woman with several life-
OL,7,Flong health problems, caused by a
OL,8,Fmedication which was prescribed to her
OL,9,Fmother while pregnant, says it has
OL,10,Fbeen a "long battle" for change and
OL,11,Frecognition of her condition.
OL,13,FBethany Dodgson has foetal valproate
OL,14,Fsyndrome which can occur when a foetus
OL,15,Fis exposed to valproic acid during
OL,16,Fpregnancy, leading to a range of birth
OL,17,Fdefects, developmental delays, and
OL,18,Fneurodevelopment issues.
