OL,6,FMs Dodgson's condition was caused by
OL,7,Fthe drug sodium valproate which was
OL,8,Fgiven to her mother to control her
OL,9,Fepileptic seizures.
OL,11,FThe medication since been linked to
OL,12,Fbirth defects and development issues
OL,13,Fin children when it is taken by their
OL,14,Fmothers while pregnant.
OL,16,FMs Dodgson said her mother was not
OL,17,Fmade aware of the risks it had for
OL,18,Fpregnant women.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
