OL,6,FThe 32-year-old said it has been a
OL,7,Flong journey to bring action for
OL,8,Fvictims of the health scandal, which
OL,9,Fis thought to have effected thousands
OL,10,Fof other children since the 1970s.
OL,12,FWhile Ms Dodgson believes that support
OL,13,Ffor those with the condition has
OL,14,F"dramatically improved" over the
OL,15,Fyears, she says there is still a long
OL,16,Fway to go.
OL,18,F"It's slowly getting there, but it's
OL,19,Fnot enough," she said.
