OL,6,F"I've had medical appointments in the
OL,7,Fpast where I've had to explain my
OL,8,Fcondition, as they don't know about
OL,9,Fthe condition.
OL,11,F"But, I did have a GP appointment last
OL,12,Fmonth and they knew all about my
OL,13,Fcondition."
OL,15,FThe 32-year-old is also a carer for
OL,16,Fher brother, who is severely impacted
OL,17,Fby the condition.
