OL,6,F"I was always be there for my brother,
OL,7,Fand make sure everything is ok for
OL,8,Fhim, and to fight the battles he can't
OL,9,Ffight," she said.
OL,11,FShe added that it's been a "long,
OL,12,Flong, battle" with "awareness,
OL,13,Fcampaigns, and reports" over the years.
OL,15,FIt is an effective treatment for
OL,16,Fepilepsy, but it's been linked to
OL,17,Flifelong disabilities in at least
OL,18,F20,000 babies whose mothers were
OL,19,Fprescribed the drug while they were
OL,20,Fpregnant.
