OL,6,FThe use of pelvic mesh for many
OL,7,Fconditions was paused in 2018 amid
OL,8,Fsafety concerns.
OL,10,FIt comes as this year marks a year on
OL,11,Fsince a review into two medical
OL,12,Fscandals, including the epilepsy
OL,13,Fmedication Sodium Valproate, as well
OL,14,Fthe use of pelvic mesh, was published.
OL,16,FEngland's Patient Safety Commissioner,
OL,17,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes, published
OL,18,FThe Hughes Report on 7 February 2024,
OL,19,Fwhich examined the impact of the two
OL,20,Fmedical controversies.
