OL,6,FThousands of women experienced severe
OL,7,Fcomplications after undergoing surgery
OL,8,Finvolving vaginal mesh implants
OL,9,Fbetween 2007 and 2015.
OL,11,FToday, the MP for Washington and
OL,12,FGateshead South, Sharon Hodgson, led a
OL,13,Fdebate in Parliament. Her mother was
OL,14,Fimpacted by the mesh scandal.
OL,16,F"It's something she says she will
OL,17,Fregret to her dying day, which I hope
OL,18,Fis still many years off," she said.
