OL,6,F"So if the Government doesn't move off
OL,7,Fthe moral case of these healthcare
OL,8,Fscandals, surely they cannot deny the
OL,9,Feconomic toll taken on our public and
OL,10,Fmental health services.
OL,12,F"So we have a decision to make, and
OL,13,Ffor me, the thousands of women and
OL,14,Fcampaigners, the answer cannot be
OL,15,Fsimpler."
